1
00:01:12,789 --> 00:01:15,750
Ahead is the Yaowang Valley's branch outside the capital.

2
00:01:15,750 --> 00:01:17,080
It is highly concealed.

3
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,250
Normally, only a few disciples are stationed there,

4
00:01:19,250 --> 00:01:20,580
along with my master.

5
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:22,910
Let's go there to take shelter for now

6
00:01:22,910 --> 00:01:24,170
and plan our next move.

7
00:01:29,450 --> 00:01:31,250
We'll settle at the branch first.

8
00:01:31,250 --> 00:01:32,500
Once we are settled,

9
00:01:32,539 --> 00:01:34,539
we will find a way to get news about Ying.

10
00:01:34,539 --> 00:01:36,539
We can't let Ying face danger alone.

11
00:01:51,910 --> 00:01:52,770
Senior Sister.

12
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:59,160
The Valley Master has been waiting for a long time.

13
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,790
Hearing that you were bringing a friend,

14
00:02:00,790 --> 00:02:02,750
she specially prepared healing herbs.

15
00:02:02,750 --> 00:02:04,280
Let's go find my master now.

16
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:17,250
Master of the Crossing Lamp, you have finally returned.

17
00:02:17,250 --> 00:02:20,180
Our Yaowang Valley has waited for you for a long time.

18
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:23,000
You know me?

19
00:02:27,329 --> 00:02:29,620
Valley Master, Ah Deng has just awakened her memories,

20
00:02:29,620 --> 00:02:30,790
and her mind is still unsettled.

21
00:02:30,790 --> 00:02:32,160
Please enlighten us, Valley Master.

22
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,829
What is the Master of the Crossing Lamp?

23
00:02:33,829 --> 00:02:35,090
Why do you know Ah Deng?

24
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,620
Master of the Crossing Lamp,

25
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,079
you may not remember,

26
00:02:42,290 --> 00:02:44,410
but every generation of successors in Yaowang Valley

27
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:45,950
remembers your kindness.

28
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:49,910
Valley Master, what exactly is this kindness you speak of?

29
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:52,370
Three hundred years ago, the mortal realm was plagued by constant war.

30
00:02:52,370 --> 00:02:53,660
Evil spirits ran rampant,

31
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:55,579
and the remnants of the Demon Tribe wreaked havoc everywhere.

32
00:02:55,579 --> 00:02:57,790
Countless commoners were harassed by evil spirits

33
00:02:57,790 --> 00:02:59,200
and suffered unspeakably.

34
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:01,950
Especially the defenseless women of that time,

35
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,580
who suffered the most.

36
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:05,790
They were treated as sacrifices for the evil spirits

37
00:03:05,790 --> 00:03:07,200
and displaced from their homes.

38
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,830
It was you who couldn't bear to see this.

39
00:03:08,830 --> 00:03:11,910
You rescued and healed a group of women harmed by evil spirits,

40
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:14,790
founded Yaowang Valley with your own spiritual power,

41
00:03:14,790 --> 00:03:16,750
and taught these women medical skills,

42
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,870
allowing them to have a place in the world.

43
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:21,930
You once said that healers save others and themselves.

44
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:25,400
The mission of Yaowang Valley is to protect the common people

45
00:03:25,450 --> 00:03:26,850
and dispel evil spirits.

46
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,829
This is in line with your heart to save the world.

47
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,829
Therefore, whenever there is a war,

48
00:03:31,829 --> 00:03:35,290
Yaowang Valley organizes its disciples to rescue the people.

49
00:03:35,329 --> 00:03:38,860
Children who lost their parents are brought back to the valley.

50
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,910
Thus, Yaowang Valley has become what it is today.

51
00:03:43,579 --> 00:03:44,440
Valley Master,

52
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:47,160
what is the reason for the Xie family

53
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:49,620
becoming lamp protectors for generations?

54
00:03:49,829 --> 00:03:54,000
The ancestors of the Xie family were loyal guards under the Creator God.

55
00:03:54,410 --> 00:03:57,660
After Lady Ah Deng and Lady Ying were born,

56
00:03:58,079 --> 00:04:02,410
the Xie family was required to protect the Master of the Crossing Lamp and the Bronze Soul Lamp for generations

57
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:05,580
to prevent the Bronze Soul Lamp from falling into the hands of evildoers.

58
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:06,980
Three hundred years ago,

59
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,620
in the great war between humans and demons,

60
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:10,450
your spiritual power was exhausted, and you began reincarnation.

61
00:04:10,450 --> 00:04:11,950
Thus, as if guided by destiny,

62
00:04:11,950 --> 00:04:14,370
someone from the Xie family would always meet you in every generation.

63
00:04:14,370 --> 00:04:17,160
This is their innate mission as lamp protectors.

64
00:04:17,329 --> 00:04:20,620
Then why did Ying and I turn against each other back then?

65
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:23,580
Previously, you and Lady Ying

66
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:25,250
never had any rift.

67
00:04:25,580 --> 00:04:26,830
But a thousand years ago,

68
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,450
the Demon Tribe secretly sowed discord,

69
00:04:28,450 --> 00:04:30,330
falsely claiming that you favored the lamp protectors

70
00:04:30,330 --> 00:04:32,080
and disregarded Lady Ying's safety.

71
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,080
They also said that you were entirely focused on protecting the mortal realm

72
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,680
and would abandon Lady Ying.

73
00:04:35,909 --> 00:04:37,970
Lady Ying was inherently sensitive,

74
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,950
and since she controlled resentment,

75
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:42,080
she was easily affected by hostility.

76
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:45,380
Over time, she developed disagreements with you.

77
00:04:45,450 --> 00:04:47,710
So there is such a hidden truth behind it.

78
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:51,700
Ah Deng, don't be sad.

79
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,409
It's all in the past.

80
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:56,080
We'll slowly find the truth in the future.

81
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:59,130
and slowly resolve the grudges between you and Ying.

82
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:03,160
I wronged Ying.

83
00:05:04,250 --> 00:05:05,160
If I hadn't

84
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:07,370
failed to notice the demons' instigation back then,

85
00:05:07,370 --> 00:05:09,500
this tragedy wouldn't have happened.

86
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:12,750
Ying must have suffered a lot these years.

87
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:16,370
Master Du, it wasn't just your fault.

88
00:05:16,660 --> 00:05:18,000
The demons' instigation

89
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,540
and the erosion of the dark mist

90
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:20,940
were also major reasons.

91
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,700
Although Ms. Ying has grievances,

92
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:26,250
she never truly wanted to hurt you.

93
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,040
Otherwise,

94
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,660
she wouldn't have

95
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:32,409
left a trace of your soul to help you reincarnate,

96
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:36,300
let alone stay behind alone to cover your retreat just now.

97
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:47,540
Sister, go!

98
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,250
The emperor allied with Qin Chong

99
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:51,909
and is leading the remnants of the demons to set up a sealing array.

100
00:05:51,909 --> 00:05:53,000
Once caught,

101
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,870
not only will the Soul Lamp be taken by Qin Chong,

102
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:56,659
but your soul will also dissipate.

103
00:05:56,659 --> 00:05:58,000
If he uses the power of the Soul Lamp

104
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,950
to awaken the main force of the demons,

105
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:01,480
the human realm will be completely finished.

106
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,000
Ying, how are you?

107
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,550
How did you get hurt so badly?

108
00:06:20,330 --> 00:06:22,410
I'm not here for your pity.

109
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:25,400
I just don't want the demons to have it easy.

110
00:06:26,580 --> 00:06:27,500
I know.

111
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,250
I know.

112
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:31,050
Let me help you sit down and rest.

113
00:06:39,659 --> 00:06:41,920
Ms. Ying, thank you for the information.

114
00:06:42,290 --> 00:06:44,330
No matter how many past grudges there are,

115
00:06:44,330 --> 00:06:46,190
our enemy right now is the demons.

116
00:06:46,659 --> 00:06:48,159
Let's leave here together first

117
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:49,080
and then plan our next move.

118
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:51,409
When Master Du founded the Medicine King Valley,

119
00:06:51,409 --> 00:06:53,940
she left a secret realm deep in the mountains.

120
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,790
There is a spiritual barrier there

121
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:59,120
that can temporarily resist the power of the sealing array.

122
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:04,080
A'Deng.

123
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,950
Let Ms. Ying take this first.

124
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:07,700
This medicine can reduce swelling, promote tissue regeneration,

125
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:08,620
and heal wounds.

126
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:09,830
Let's set off immediately.

127
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,430
Any delay may cause trouble.

128
00:07:23,540 --> 00:07:24,830
My spiritual power can also

129
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:26,290
accelerate the healing of your wounds.
